Random seems more fun but yeah, it adds luck to a game that isn&#39;t supposed to have much luck at all. I like picking my pieces. Here&#39;s my preferred starting hand which has won 50% of games so far:<br />
<br />
4 strength High Helmet<br />
4 strength Budda<br />
4 Strength Rice Field<br />
3 strength Samurai<br />
2 strength Ship<br />
